# Marvel Character Full-Stack Application

A React + Flask + MySQL CRUD app to manage Marvel heroes and villains.  
Built as a full-stack portfolio project for Coding Temple / Full Stack curriculum.

---

## 🚀 Features

- **View** all Marvel characters in a responsive card grid
- **View details** of each character (powers, alignment, alias, image)
- **Add** new characters with image and traits
- **Edit** any character (pre-filled form, instant update)
- **Delete** characters with confirmation
- **Clean navigation** with React Bootstrap Navbar and 404 routing
- **Mobile friendly** (Bootstrap grid)

